    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305590/extras/bb0a88244388ff3d8a0e33a29d392bd9.avif?t=1749386811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305590/extras_big/bb0a88244388ff3d8a0e33a29d392bd9.avif?t=1749386811 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HELLCAM IS AN ENVIRONMENTAL DEMO! The purpose of this demo is to showcase the high-quality visuals which is soon to be a full game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HELLCAM</strong> is an indie psychological horror exploration game developed in Unreal Engine 5. You wont find any lackluster objectives, instead oppressive <strong>liminal spaces</strong> are designed in order to make you feel stranded.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305590/extras/3472662d0ce7c7b6b5bd6bd4f6e5029a.avif?t=1749386811\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multiple different ultra-realistic and stranded liminal spaces throughout the game, some places seeming more familiar then others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305590/extras/9f372b9a9f844658759969afc5777c67.avif?t=1749386811\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>HELLCAM</strong>, you follow a backrooms researcher through the lens of a VHS camera. As you explore the unsettling, endless halls, you uncover the dark truth behind a <strong>corrupt corporation</strong> that sends its workers into the backrooms, knowing they’ll never make it out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305590/extras/f9ac5df9fd34450a7a62e574b78efc5f.avif?t=1749386811\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience an immersive journey with the classic look of the <strong>1980s</strong>, combined with the <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong> engine to create a hyper-realistic expedition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
